TPS659037 Regulator description structure.

Field Documentation

uint32_t pmhalTps659037RegulatorProp::ctrlRegAddr

The regulator control register address.

uint32_t pmhalTps659037RegulatorProp::forceRegAddr

The regulator force command voltage register address. Not all regulators have the force register; if not present the value of this field is expected to be NULL.

uint16_t pmhalTps659037RegulatorProp::maxVolt

Maximum voltage supported by the regulator in mV.

uint16_t pmhalTps659037RegulatorProp::maxVoltVsel

VSEL value corresponding to the maxVolt.

uint16_t pmhalTps659037RegulatorProp::minVolt

Minimum voltage supported by the regulator in mV.

uint16_t pmhalTps659037RegulatorProp::minVoltVsel

VSEL value corresponding to the minVolt.

uint16_t pmhalTps659037RegulatorProp::slewRate

The voltage ramp delay in uV/us

uint8_t pmhalTps659037RegulatorProp::stepVolt

Step voltage in mV.

uint8_t pmhalTps659037RegulatorProp::type

The regulator type namely PMHAL_TPS659037_RTYPE_SMPS or PMHAL_TPS659037_RTYPE_LDO.

uint32_t pmhalTps659037RegulatorProp::voltRegAddr

The regulator voltage register address.
